node_7.subject: Maria Lopez
node_7.description: This is Maria Lopez's plan for Monday February 13: wake up and complete the morning routine at 8:00 am, read a scientific paper and take notes at 9:00 am, prepare and organize the presentation based on the paper at 10:00 am, practice the presentation and make any necessary changes at 11:00 am, have lunch and take a short break at 12:00 pm, give the presentation to a group of colleagues at 1:00 pm, engage in discussions about the paper with the colleagues after the presentation at 2:00 pm, continue working on any revisions or additional research related to the paper at 3:00 pm.
